section.para:
The Tracker project was undertaken to provide;




			A useful service for livestock producers and
			infrastructure providers;





			A low cost solution to enable both large and
			small scale deployment;





			An industry standard for livestock event history
			inter-exchange.

Animals and Events are added to Tracker Premises Documents;




			Individually by the user via the Tracker Premise Document Editor and Properties Viewer;





			In bulk, by the user, through Tracker's Bulk Event Processing Utilities;





			In real time, from RFID readers, through the Tracker Transaction Processing Facility.
